summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 16708 entitled: "An ordinance relating to and providing for the improvement of 16th Avenue in the City of Seattle, from East Alder Street to East Cherry Street, by constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, all in accordance with Resolution No. 721 of the city council of the City of Seattle; and providing payment therefor by the mode of "Payment in Bonds", as provided by the laws of the State of Washington and the Charter and Ordinances of the City of Seattle."
